Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP14.client.view.gui.scenes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GUIFirstPlayerScene
    A view that allows a player to choose the player who goes first in the match.
    GUIGameScene
    A view representing the board, player info, gods info.
    GUIGodSelectScene
    A view that allows the players to choose the god they'll use in a match.
    GUILobbySizeScene
    This scene asks the user who created the lobby to define the size of the lobby (2 or 3 players)
    GUIUsernameScene
    This scene asks the user to input the username to be used in the game.
    GUIWelcomeScene
    Welcome screen loaded while connecting to the server.
    NotificationScene
    Toast-like notification to notify the user of minor details.
